Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:01.06,1080P-shsm-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\pos(960,1020)}你可能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:02.57,1080P-shsb-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}getting to the moon isn't as simple as
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:02.57,1080P-shsm-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\pos(960,1020)}登上月球不是简单地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:06.59,1080P-shsb-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}just pointing a rocket straight up blasting into space and slowing down when you get to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:06.59,1080P-shsm-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\pos(960,1020)}把火箭指向太空发射 到了月球再减速就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:09.40,1080P-shsb-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Getting to the moon is not a straight shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:09.40,1080P-shsm-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\pos(960,1020)}到达月球不是直着去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:13.92,1080P-shsb-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It requires some orbital mechanics and a few maneuvers to precisely get you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:13.92,1080P-shsm-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\pos(960,1020)}它需要一些轨道力学和一些机动动作来精确地把你送到那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:16.42,1080P-shsb-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So we're going to show you the mission profiles here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:16.42,1080P-shsm-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\pos(960,1020)}所以我们要在这里给大家看一下任务概况
