Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:18.71,1080P-shsm-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\pos(960,1020)}这里有一个小插曲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:22.75,1080P-shsb-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}This is going to be kind of the eventual ish standard flight profile of
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:22.75,1080P-shsm-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\pos(960,1020)}这将是一种最终的标准飞行概况
