Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:51.31,1080P-shsb-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}our timeline and our numbers are probably going to be a little bit off
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:51.31,1080P-shsm-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\pos(960,1020)}接下来要讲的时间表和数据可能是有点偏差的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:54.36,1080P-shsb-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}because Artemis doesn't even have these things published yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:54.36,1080P-shsm-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\pos(960,1020)}因为阿尔忒弥斯还没公布这些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:57.80,1080P-shsb-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And the first two or three missions will probably be quite a bit different than this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:57.80,1080P-shsm-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\pos(960,1020)}而且前两三个任务可能会和这个有很大的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:16:59.32,1080P-shsb-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but this is just a generic
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:16:59.32,1080P-shsm-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\pos(960,1020)}但这只是一个通用的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:04.09,1080P-shsb-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}what eventually Artemis will likely be doing to get into that near rectilinear halo orbit,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:04.09,1080P-shsm-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\pos(960,1020)}阿尔忒弥斯最终可能要做的就是进入那个近直线晕轮轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:07.74,1080P-shsb-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but even our Apollo profile here is kind of generic
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:10.81,1080P-shsb-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}since each and every mission had some unique variances.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:07.74,1080P-shsm-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\pos(960,1020)}但即使是我们这里的阿波罗资料 也是一种通用的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:10.81,1080P-shsm-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\pos(960,1020)}因为每个任务都有一些独特的差异
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:14.86,1080P-shsb-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So let's put both missions together and compare them side by side,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:14.86,1080P-shsm-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\pos(960,1020)}所以 我们把这两个任务放在一起 进行并列比较 (比较具有代表性)
