Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:35.32,1080P-shsm-7u,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}土星五号在起飞时(前) 当然使用的是五台强大的F1发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:39.26,1080P-shsb-5u,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The SLS will fire up its four RS-25 main engines,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:39.26,1080P-shsm-7u,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而SLS将启动四台RS-25主发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:43.22,1080P-shsb-5u,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and then light it's massive solid rocket boosters when it's time to go.
